covCathedral_Report.bio: AT THE COVENTRY MUSIC MUSEUM, WE TELL THE REAL STORY OF OUR MUSICAL HERITAGE, GOING RIGHT BACK TO THE ROMAN OCCUPATION.WE STOP ALONG THE WAY AT MUSIC HALL, 50’S ROCK ’N’ ROLL, THE 60’S BEAT SCENE & WE EVEN HAVE THE LENNON BENCH, COMMEMORATING THE FAMOUS ‘ACORNS FOR PEACE’ EVENT.
covCathedral_Report.title: The Coventry Music Museum
